thread.title: Kathy B

author: Kathy B
title: Kathy B
text: I could not find Andy's Candies in bulk at a good price anywhere - and then I came across this website! Price was very good (much cheaper than one at a time or in small packages) and ordered them. I had not planned on spending that much on candy, but was delighted that I wouldn't have to go buy candy each week. They arrived before the scheduled time and are absolutely perfect! Thank you S much! I will be ordering more when my supply gets low if they are still available!
